<h3><a name="BSICS_Computing_Support_Contact"></a>BSICS
Computing
Support Contact Information: &nbsp;</h3>
<br>
<br>
The BSICS Computing Support Group can be contacted by email at
&nbsp;&lt;helpdesk@ics.uci.edu&gt; and by phone at
(949)824-4222.
&nbsp;Normal business hours for the group are from
9am-5pm.&nbsp; Both
the helpdesk email and voice mail are monitored during off hours.
<br>
<br>
More information about BSICS Computing Support is available at the
following URL:
<br>
<br>
<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><a
 href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/computing/contact/helpdesk.php">http://www.ics.uci.edu/computing/contact/helpdesk.php</a><br>
<br>
<br>
</div>
Please Note: &nbsp;If you believe that there is a problem with
email or
that an email message to helpdesk would not be processed by the BSICS
email servers, &nbsp;please&nbsp;call the helpdesk at
(949)824-4222.&nbsp; <br>
